## Fixture Wiring Check (MANDATORY after fixture changes)

After any cleanup that **adds, renames, or removes a fixture property**, or that modifies `scenario-test-fixture.ts`, run a quick smoke test to verify nothing is broken:

```bash
PLAYWRIGHT_RETRIES=0 npx playwright test \
  --config=playwright/playwright.config.ts \
  --grep "@gating" \
  --workers=1 \
  --reporter=list 2>&1
```

A passing gating run confirms the fixture wiring is intact — gating tests exercise the full fixture chain including `k8sClient`, `testConfig`, `cleanup`, and `utils`.

